---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | GrowthGrid" description="Read our terms of service and usage guidelines.">
  <Header />
  <main class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 transition-colors">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8 uppercase tracking-tight">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        <p class="mb-6 italic">Last Updated: April 28, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          By accessing and using <strong>GrowthGrid</strong>, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our site.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">2. Use of Calculators</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Our financial tools and calculators are provided for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. They do not constitute professional financial advice. Always consult with a certified financial advisor before making significant financial decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">3. Accuracy of Data</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          While we strive for high precision, we do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any results produced by our tools. 
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          All content, including tools, text, and design, is the property of GrowthGrid. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without explicit permission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
